RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT B.CONTRACT_REF_NO,A.MATURITY_DATE,B.USER_REF_NO,B.CUSTOM_REF_NO,B.COUNTERPARTY,B.USER_DEFINED_STATUS,B.CONTRACT_STATUS,B.CONTRACT_CCY,B.LATEST_VERSION_NO,C.CUSTOMER_NAME1,D.PRINCIPAL_OUTSTANDING_BAL,D.RESERVE_AMT,D.FAS114_RESERVE_AMT,A.BRANCH,E.BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B, OLTMS_CUSTOMER C, OLTBS_CONTRACT_BALANCE D ,OLTMS_BRANCH E WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.VERSION_NO = B.LATEST_VERSION_NO AND B.COUNTERPARTY = C.CUSTOMER_NO AND B.CONTRACT_REF_NO = D.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.BRANCH = E.BRANCH_CODE AND B.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND B.MODULE_CODE ='OL'

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONTRACT_REF_NO) IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = PRODUCT_CODE AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
